OL,3,CCeiling collapse takes nearly a month
OL,4,Cto fix
OL,6,FA mother of two from Cornwall has
OL,7,Fspent more than three weeks waiting
OL,8,Ffor repairs to be completed to her
OL,9,Fson's bedoom after the ceiling
OL,10,Fcollapsed.
OL,12,FIt led to water pouring into the
OL,13,Fproperty, and has has to be fully
OL,14,Ffixed by contractors.
OL,16,FVicki told ITV News: "The ceiling came
OL,17,Fdown on the 31st of January at about
OL,18,F11pm. I was sat downstairs and heard a
OL,19,Fmassive bang. I came running upstairs
OL,20,Fand the ceiling was falling down
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772132672
OL,3,CCeiling collapse takes nearly a month
OL,4,Cto fix
OL,6,F"I went into panic mode and got
OL,7,Fstraight onto the phone to the
OL,8,FGuinness Partnerships repairs line."
OL,10,FVicki says her home has been turned
OL,11,F"upside down" as a result, with her
OL,12,Fson sleeping in her room and Vicki
OL,13,Fstill sleeping on the settee in the
OL,14,Fliving room.
OL,16,FVicki says that despite reporting the
OL,17,Fissue immediately, nearly a month on
OL,18,Fthe issue is still yet to be fully
OL,19,Ffixed.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
