CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772132672
OL,3,CCeiling collapse takes nearly a month
OL,4,Cto fix
OL,6,FShe said: "I'd like to have a house I
OL,7,Fcan live in, and not be afraid that a
OL,8,Fceiling is going to fall down or the
OL,9,Fback door is going to break, and I've
OL,10,Fgot water and damp coming into my
OL,11,Fhome. I want a safe environment for my
OL,12,Fchildren."
OL,14,FIn July 2025 we interviewed Vicki as
OL,15,Fshe had an issue with the ceiling of
OL,16,Fher daughter's bedroom which took many
OL,17,Fmonths to be fixed.
OL,19,FVicki says she feels she is being
OL,20,Fignored by her housing provider, the
OL,21,FGuinness Partnership.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772132672
OL,3,CCeiling collapse takes nearly a month
OL,4,Cto fix
OL,6,FThe Guinness Partnership were
OL,7,Fcontacted by ITV West Country News on
OL,8,Fthe 19th of February. On the 20th of
OL,9,FFebruary, according to Vicki,
OL,10,Fscaffolding was erected at her
OL,11,Fproperty and repairs are still under
OL,12,Funderway (as of 26th February), but
OL,13,Fnot yet complete.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for The Guinness
OL,16,FPartnership said: "Following our
OL,17,Frepairs to a small area of the roof in
OL,18,Fmid 2025, an inspection of the whole
OL,19,Froof indicated that it was sound.
OL,26,@xD@SOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772132672
OL,3,CCeiling collapse takes nearly a month
OL,4,Cto fix
OL,6,F"Our survey of the source of the
OL,7,Frecent leak, indicates damage during
OL,8,Frecent extreme storm weather. As soon
OL,9,Fas we were made aware of this
OL,10,Fincident, we sent emergency
OL,11,Fcontractors to the home to ensure
OL,12,Feveryone was safe and to assess the
OL,13,Fdamage. It has now been repaired. We
OL,14,Fapologise profusely for the three week
OL,15,Fdelay while we secured the services of
OL,16,Fa roofer.
OL,18,F"A new back door has also been ordered
OL,19,Fand again we apologise for the delay
OL,20,Fassociated with this."
OL,26,@|D@VO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
