OL,3,CCeiling collapse takes nearly a month
OL,4,Cto fix
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Cornwall Council
OL,7,Fsaid: "Social housing landlords are
OL,8,Fresponsible for managing and
OL,9,Fmaintaining their properties in
OL,10,Faccordance with standards set out by
OL,11,Fthe Regulator of Social Housing. In
OL,12,Fcircumstances where tenants are not
OL,13,Fsatisfied with the response from their
OL,14,Flandlord, they can request the Housing
OL,15,FOmbudsman intervene.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
